snippet: Brittney Griner scored the game’s first 5 points and finished with 23 as host Baylor led throughout in its first game since taking back the No. 1 spot, defeating 25th-ranked Iowa State, 67-39.
abstract: Baylor defeats Iowa State, 67-39, in women's college basketball; other scores noted.
